PN,34901
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FBaroness Amos says she is "concerned
OL,8,Fabout safety for women, birthing
OL,9,Fpeople and babies" at Sandwell and
OL,10,FWest Birmingham NHS Trust.
OL,12,FThe Trust, which provides maternity
OL,13,Fservices at the Midland Metropolitan
OL,14,FUniversity Hospital, was one of 12
OL,15,Faround the country to be given a
OL,16,Fbespoke report as part of Baroness
OL,17,FAmos's nationwide maternity review.
OL,19,FThe 23 pages paint a damning picture
OL,20,Fof maternity and neonatal care.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34902
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThey reveal that the inspection team
OL,8,Fheard evidence of widespread racism
OL,9,Fand discrimination and even witnessed
OL,10,Fan incident of racism on their visit.
OL,12,FClinical staff raised concerns about
OL,13,Fthe safety of the parents and babies
OL,14,Fin their care. Some had left because
OL,15,Fthey didn't believe they were
OL,16,Fproviding a safe service.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThere was "visible tension in how
OL,8,Fstaff spoke to each other" with
OL,9,F"inequality and racist behaviour were
OL,10,Fsometimes spoken about casually as if
OL,11,Fit was part of the day-to-day."
OL,13,FLeadership was criticised, with staff
OL,14,Fsaying there was a culture of avoiding
OL,15,Fdealing with discriminatory behaviour
OL,16,Frather than dealing with it.
OL,18,FStaffing levels, parents not being
OL,19,Flistened to and families saying they
OL,20,Ffelt "powerless" to raise concerns
OL,21,Fwere also raised as issues.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34904
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe report concludes that Baroness
OL,8,FAmos remains "concerned about cultural
OL,9,Fissues, local procedures and how they
OL,10,Fimpact on the safety of parents and
OL,11,Fbabies at the Trust."
OL,13,FBaroness Amos chose the 12 Trusts each
OL,14,Ffor different reasons, so as to
OL,15,Finclude a diverse mix of hospitals.
OL,17,FSandwell and West Birmingham NHS Trust
OL,18,Fhas a high rate of neonatal deaths
OL,19,F(deaths within the first 27 days of
OL,20,Flife). The report shows it is five per
OL,21,Fcent higher than the national average.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34905
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe Trust's maternity and neonatal
OL,8,Fservices were both rated as "Requires
OL,9,FImprovement" by the Care Quality
OL,10,FCommission (CQC) in February 2026,
OL,11,Fwhich is unchanged from their rating
OL,12,Fback in November 2024.
OL,14,FThe Trust also serves a diverse
OL,15,Fcommunity. Compared to the national
OL,16,Faverage, it provides services to more
OL,17,FAsian and Black mothers, alongside a
OL,18,Fwide range of other backgrounds,
OL,19,Fcultures, and ethnicities. The area
OL,20,Fthat is also more deprived than 91% of
OL,21,Fneighbourhoods in England.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G5/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34906
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThe report shows that this community
OL,8,Fisn't being served fairly, with Amos
OL,9,Fsaying that the care families receives
OL,10,Fvaries depending on their ethnicity or
OL,11,Fbackground. Some families said that
OL,12,Ftheir care would have been better if
OL,13,Fstaff had not judged them or delivered
OL,14,Fcare based on their race. Meanwhile, a
OL,15,Fwhite family told investigators about
OL,16,Fwitnessing an Asian family being
OL,17,Ftreated differently and spoken down to
OL,18,Fby the same staff members who treated
OL,19,Fthem with respect and kindness.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FStaff also experienced unequal
OL,8,Ftreatment and racism from within the
OL,9,FTrust. Issues raised at the
OL,10,Finvestigators' first visit in January
OL,11,Fled to a second visit taking place to
OL,12,Fmet solely with staff from ethnic
OL,13,Fminority backgrounds, where these
OL,14,Fconcerns were raised.
OL,16,FThe report does acknowledge that the
OL,17,Fservices are now based from a brand
OL,18,Fnew hospital, which many staff said
OL,19,Fhad helped provide better care to
OL,20,Fpatients and allowed for better
OL,21,Ffacilities.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G7/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34908
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FMidland Metropolitan University
OL,8,FHospital opened in 2024, replacing
OL,9,FCity Hospital and Sandwell General
OL,10,FHospital
OL,12,FThe report also says that the Trust's
OL,13,FExecutive Team has described plans to
OL,14,Fimprove communication, services and
OL,15,Fsupport for families including work
OL,16,Fwith faith groups and to increase
OL,17,Funderstanding of practical support
OL,18,Fsuch as sim cards and signposts to
OL,19,Ffood banks for families in need.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G8/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FBaroness Amos's team were also told
OL,8,Fthat the leadership and governance
OL,9,Fsystem were undergoing changes and
OL,10,Fimprovements were underway to address
OL,11,Fissues such as communication
OL,12,Fbreakdowns with patients and
OL,13,Fdiscriminatory behaviour,
OL,15,FThe Trust has also today apologised.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G9/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34910
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FIn an open letter to patients they
OL,8,Fsaid "we are sorry to the women,
OL,9,Fbabies and families whose experiences
OL,10,Fof our maternity and neonatal services
OL,11,Fdid not meet the standards they have
OL,12,Fthe right to expect. The report
OL,13,Fhighlights areas where our care fell
OL,14,Fshort, and we recognise the lasting
OL,15,Fand profound impact this has had on
OL,16,Fthose affected."
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G10/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BC Eng News CThis Day FReg TV
FL,350,340,120,260,000,100
PN,34911
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F349A1782908304
OL,3,CAmos 'concerned about safety' of
OL,4,Cparents and babies at Smethwick
OL,5,Chospital
OL,7,FThey also said they are "particularly
OL,8,Fappalled" by the accounts of racism
OL,9,Fand discrimination described within
OL,10,Fthe report and that they are
OL,11,Fdetermined to learn from it.
OL,13,FPatients who have experienced poor
OL,14,Fcare have told ITV News Central they
OL,15,Fhope this is the case, and they want
OL,16,Fto see that change happen now.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4         G11/11
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
